Name: The Mysterious Gift
Title: You will trade five unique items with a vendor.

Name: Strong as a Bull
Title: You will track down a powerful Fighting Bull who will drop a unique item when slain.

Name: The Cursed Choir
Title: You will discover an area with large packs of Sea Witches.

Name: Overflowing Riches
Title: You will slay a foe who erupts into currency.

Name: The Dream Trial
Title: You will discover a Trial of Ascendancy in a map.
